### Phase 4: E2E Tests Implementation
We will create the following test files inside `catchupx-v1/e2e/`:

#### [NEW] [sms-flows.spec.ts](file:///c:/Coding/CatchupXV1/catchupx-v1/e2e/sms-flows.spec.ts)
- **Announcement Flow:** Login as teacher, create an announcement, login as student, verify visibility.
- **Live Classroom Flow:** Login as teacher, start session, start poll. Login as student (in a separate browser context), join session, submit answer, signal confusion. Teacher verifies results and heatmap update.
- **Report Card Flow:** Create and finalize a report card, verify student can view and download.
- **Gamification & Leaderboard:** Verify XP stats, badges, and leaderboard filtering.
- **Exam Predictor:** Verify score predictions, topics, and risk radar rendering.

#### [NEW] [responsive.spec.ts](file:///c:/Coding/CatchupXV1/catchupx-v1/e2e/responsive.spec.ts)
