- Verify the navigation menu toggles correctly on mobile.

#### [NEW] [accessibility.spec.ts](file:///c:/Coding/CatchupXV1/catchupx-v1/e2e/accessibility.spec.ts)
- Integrate `@axe-core/playwright`.
- Automatically scan the main pages for WCAG violations (e.g., missing ARIA labels, low contrast, focus issues).

